    <div class="flex flex-col gap-10 pt-12 w-[626px] max-md:w-full">
        <article class="flex flex-col gap-6 max-sm:gap-4">
            <header class="flex gap-3 items-center max-sm:flex-col max-sm:gap-4 max-sm:items-start">
                <div class="treatment-icon-container">
                    <svg
                        width="56"
                        height="56"
                        viewBox="0 0 56 56"
                        fill="none"
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                        class="treatment-icon"
                        style="width: 56px; height: 56px; flex-shrink: 0"
                    >
                        <defs>
                            <clipPath id="clip0_469_333">
                                <rect width="56" height="56" fill="white"></rect>
                            </clipPath>
                        </defs>
                        <g clip-path="url(#clip0_469_333)">
                            <path
                                d="M56 28C56 12.536 43.464 0 28 0C12.536 0 0 12.536 0 28C0 43.464 12.536 56 28 56C43.464 56 56 43.464 56 28Z"
                                fill="#222222"
                            ></path>
                            <text
                                fill="white"
                                xml:space="preserve"
                                style="white-space: pre"
                                font-family="Inter"
                                font-size="22.4"
                                font-weight="bold"
                                letter-spacing="0em"
                            >
                                <tspan x="15.7098" y="36.1457">01</tspan>
                            </text>
                        </g>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold leading-10 text-neutral-800 max-md:text-3xl max-md:leading-9 max-sm:text-2xl max-sm:leading-8 font-poppins">
                    Medication Management
                </h2>
            </header>
            <p class="text-base leading-6 text-neutral-800 max-sm:text-sm max-sm:leading-5 font-inter">
                Antidepressant medications, Regular monitoring and adjustments, Side effect management and Combination therapy when needed
            </p>
        </article>

        <article class="flex flex-col gap-6 max-sm:gap-4">
            <header class="flex gap-3 items-center max-sm:flex-col max-sm:gap-4 max-sm:items-start">
                <div class="treatment-icon-container">
                    <svg
                        width="56"
                        height="56"
                        viewBox="0 0 56 56"
                        fill="none"
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                        class="treatment-icon"
                        style="width: 56px; height: 56px; flex-shrink: 0"
                    >
                        <defs>
                            <clipPath id="clip0_469_341">
                                <rect width="56" height="56" fill="white"></rect>
                            </clipPath>
                        </defs>
                        <g clip-path="url(#clip0_469_341)">
                            <path
                                d="M56 28C56 12.536 43.464 0 28 0C12.536 0 0 12.536 0 28C0 43.464 12.536 56 28 56C43.464 56 56 43.464 56 28Z"
                                fill="#222222"
                            ></path>
                            <text
                                fill="white"
                                xml:space="preserve"
                                style="white-space: pre"
                                font-family="Inter"
                                font-size="22.4"
                                font-weight="bold"
                                letter-spacing="0em"
                            >
                                <tspan x="13.6348" y="36.1457">02</tspan>
                            </text>
                        </g>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold leading-10 text-neutral-800 max-md:text-3xl max-md:leading-9 max-sm:text-2xl max-sm:leading-8 font-poppins">
                    Transcranial Magnetic Stimulation (TMS)
                </h2>
            </header>
            <p class="text-base leading-6 text-neutral-800 max-sm:text-sm max-sm:leading-5 font-inter">
                FDA-approved non-invasive treatment, Particularly effective for treatment-resistant depression, No anesthesia required and Minimal side effects
            </p>
        </article>

        <article class="flex flex-col gap-6 max-sm:gap-4">
            <header class="flex gap-3 items-center max-sm:flex-col max-sm:gap-4 max-sm:items-start">
                <div class="treatment-icon-container">
                    <svg
                        width="56"
                        height="56"
                        viewBox="0 0 56 56"
                        fill="none"
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                        class="treatment-icon"
                        style="width: 56px; height: 56px; flex-shrink: 0"
                    >
                        <defs>
